==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hydroxyproline
<hw>hydroxyproline</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A crystalline amino acid
(<chform>C5H9NO3</chform>), a hydroxylated proline, obtained by
hydrolysis of gelatin or collagen. Chemically it is
<chname>4-hydroxy-L-proline</chname>. It is classified as nonessential
for growth in rats.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hydrozoa</ent>⟦br⟧
